altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 34
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 34
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v34 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of the following: - Naruto: Clash of Ninja - Super Mario Strikers - Chibi-Robo!, - Sonic Riders The disc also features videos of the following: - Odama - Metroid Prime - Hunters (DS) - FIFA Street 2 - Major League Baseball 2K6 - Chibi-Robo! - Sonic Riders - Curious George - ESRB ratings video
